author: Sergio Bustos, Associated Press
title: Rubio: Dem presidential debate 'like something from 1985'
text: Photo: Jim Cole, AP Republican presidential candidate Sen. Marco Rubio, R-Fla. speaks during a town hall campaign stop, Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015, in Derry, N.H. Republican presidential candidate Sen. Marco Rubio, R-Fla. speaks... PORTSMOUTH, N.H. (AP) — Republican presidential candidate Marco Rubio said Wednesday that the Democrats' presidential debate showcased old government solutions and suggested that his older rivals with names like Bush and Clinton are out of touch with most Americans.
